1
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:12,000
Really?

2
00:00:15,840 --> 00:00:19,300
They are all modeled after Qingcheng's personal belongings.

3
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,600
Even the patterns on my old belongings that were stolen in Dongxing

4
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,660
were on that paper.

5
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,520
After Chu Shengyi got the Qionghua seeds,

6
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:29,380
I followed him,

7
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:32,360
and saw him give a stack of drawings to an artisan.

8
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,760
On those drawings

9
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:36,680
were all of Qingcheng's personal belongings.

10
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:38,920
Third... Third Master.

11
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,180
What is he trying to do?

12
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,840
Logically speaking,

13
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:43,840
he is so obsessed with Xin'er.

14
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:46,400
If he wanted Qingcheng as a substitute,

15
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:49,160
he should make Qingcheng imitate Xin'er.

16
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:49,960
That's right.

17
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,400
Looking at it now,

18
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,280
it doesn't seem like he's looking for a substitute.

19
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,880
This is very suspicious.

20
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,330
There's one more thing.

21
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:00,720
This is...

22
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:03,320
Later at the black market,

23
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,780
I went to that stall again.

24
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:10,200
A fake made of rouge mixed with glue,

25
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,400
and you dare ask for a hundred guan?

26
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,840
You have a good eye, My Lady.

27
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,880
This is exclusively for the royal family.

28
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,680
You won't see the real thing outside.

29
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,210
If you hadn't seen it, boss,

30
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,570
you couldn't have imitated it so well.

31
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,010
Give it to me.

32
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:24,039
You are very clever, my lady.

33
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,880
But this rouge box is an extraordinary item.

34
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,560
It was originally

35
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:30,420
rewarded by the Grand Commander to Concubine Zhao.

36
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,000
The biological mother of the Third Young Master,

37
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,930
Concubine Zhao.

38
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:34,539
Yes.

39
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,479
After Concubine Zhao passed away,

40
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:39,640
this item eventually fell into my hands after many years.

41
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,100
But after all these years,

42
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:44,080
the rouge box was severely damaged over time.

43
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,400
If you really want to buy it, my lady,

44
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,920
I can bring out the authentic one

45
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,780
and sell it to you at a lower price.

46
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,840
It's a deal.

47
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,080
Copper rusts easily.

48
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,720
But no matter how long it has been or how easily it rusts,

49
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,320
it shouldn't look like this.

50
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,640
And these small holes are...

51
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,200
Poison.

52
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,930
But as for what poison it is,

53
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,360
I am not sure yet.

54
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,420
Could it be that

55
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:08,810
the Third Master's biological mother was poisoned?

56
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,120
This deep Marquis's mansion

57
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,080
truly eats people alive.

58
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,320
My lady,

59
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,320
after the matter of the Qionghua flower is over,

60
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,800
we'd better leave quickly.

61
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,720
Granny, please do me a favor.

62
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,770
Go and look into this poison for me.

63
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,260
Make sure no one finds out.

64
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,720
Okay.

65
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:29,360
I'm too involved with Chu Shengyi.

66
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,000
This copper rouge box

67
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,940
might become the key to saving my life in the future.

68
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,320
My lord is in such a hurry to run an errand.

69
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:47,360
I just want to remind you

70
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,680
not to rush out.

71
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,050
Young Master, Nanny Chang is here.

72
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,520
Madam asked me to bring a message.

73
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,200
The other day,

74
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:06,000
the Zhaoyebai presented by Lady Fang

75
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:08,160
pleased me very much.

76
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:11,880
Lady Fang's exquisite flower-planting skills

77
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:15,380
are unmatched by any craftsman in the Governor's Mansion.

78
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,800
Now I order the Third Master and Lady Fang

79
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,600
to plant Qionghua flowers in the mansion.

80
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,680
If they can make this flower bloom successfully,

81
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,400
I will reward them handsomely.

82
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,920
If the planting is fruitless,

83
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,560
then

84
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:34,400
everyone in the mansion will be punished for deception,

85
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:37,000
with no leniency.

86
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:40,140
I will do my best to tend to the Qionghua flowers,

87
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,060
and will never disappoint Mother's high hopes.

88
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,840
What does my lord say?

89
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:52,220
I will strictly follow Mother's instructions.

90
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,960
Then please, my lord,

91
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,050
give me the Qionghua seeds.

92
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,680
Then I will quietly wait

93
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,600
for the good news from you and Lady Fang.

94
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,530
Nice trick, my lady.

95
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,000
I had no choice.

96
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,880
After all, you fear nothing,

97
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,640
but you only listen to Mother.

98
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:37,480
I was just taking advantage of the situation.

99
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,260
Now that Mother has ordered us to plant flowers,

100
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,580
why don't we cooperate

101
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,520
and take what we need?

102
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,040
Why should I cooperate with you?

103
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,880
I said that when Qionghua blooms,

104
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,210
Qingcheng will appear.

105
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,840
In this matter,

106
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,560
our goals are the same.

107
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,880
When Concubine Zhao was alive,

108
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:01,200
the few Qionghua flowers in the private garden of Qiwu Courtyard

109
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,260
were tended by her.

110
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,080
As Concubine Zhao's son,

111
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,760
you must know the accurate planting method.

112
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,360
And I,

113
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,680
having never planted Qionghua flowers,

114
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,200
will inevitably make mistakes.

115
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,160
It doesn't matter if I die then,

116
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,040
but I fear that Mother, in her fury,

117
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,970
will implicate the whole mansion.

118
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,720
Qionghua grows faster than ordinary flowers.

119
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,580
Go buy some rootless water first.

120
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,170
Shopkeeper,

121
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:39,080
do you have rootless water for planting flowers?

122
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:41,000
Yes, yes, yes. Today's snow water is very clean.

123
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,880
I saved a lot

124
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,960
in the cellar.

125
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,920
How much do you need, my lady?

126
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,600
Just fill this bamboo tube.

127
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,960
Okay, just a moment.

128
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,280
This is so beautiful.

129
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,680
Would you like to buy one?

130
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,409
Sweep the board.

131
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,040
You.

132
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,640
Sir,

133
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:01,160
what kind of board game are you playing?

134
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,480
This is Shuanglu Chess.

135
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,240
Are you also interested?

136
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,920
I happened to see an endgame before,

137
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,500
and I have some doubts.

138
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,800
I take the liberty to ask,

139
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,560
please enlighten me.

140
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,000
I wouldn't dare.

141
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,240
It's rare to see a young lady

142
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,640
interested in Shuanglu Chess.

143
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,840
Just tell me your questions.

144
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,040
May I?

145
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,840
Please.

146
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:38,080
Brilliant.

147
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,760
Where have you seen this endgame?

148
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,680
What is so brilliant about it?

149
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:46,240
This is a deadly trap of substitution.

150
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,120
Logically,

151
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:55,000
he is obsessed with Xin'er.

152
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:57,480
If he wanted Qingcheng as a substitute,

153
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,330
he should've asked her to imitate Xin'er.

154
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,480
Looking at it now,

155
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:06,000
it doesn't seem like looking for a substitute.

156
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,360
A deadly trap.

157
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:11,730
The person in the portrait looks so much like Qingcheng.

158
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,660
Could it be?

159
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,760
Substitution.

160
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,200
Chu Shengyi wants Xin'er

161
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,920
to take his wife's place.

162
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,000
Kill his wife and replace her.

163
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,440
Young Master.

164
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,760
A body was found in the back mountain.

165
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,560
It seems to be Fang Qingcheng's.

166
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,200
Go fetch Weirui.

167
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:10,440
Yes.

168
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,600
Wait.

169
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,970
Bring Fang Zhuozhuo along as well.

170
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,280
Where did the body come from?

171
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,980
Don't worry, Miss.

172
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,480
She has been dead for days.

173
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,680
It's an unclaimed body.

174
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,000
There won't be any problems.

175
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,240
We can only wrong this lady for now.

176
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,780
After testing him,

177
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,400
we will give her a proper burial.

178
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,159
Yes.

179
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,520
Step forward and take a look.

180
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:58,240
I can't see the face clearly.

181
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,320
But the day the Pavilion Master disappeared,

182
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,850
she was wearing this dress,

183
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,660
and the figure is similar.

184
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,340
Did your Pavilion Master have

185
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,600
any distinct scars

186
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,200
or birthmarks?

187
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,720
I'm not sure.

188
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,640
But we couldn't find her for so long.

189
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,700
In all likelihood,

190
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,680
this is the Pavilion Master.

191
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,680
Pavilion Master.

192
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,560
You promised us

193
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,760
to bring back the best Jinlumei.

194
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,040
How could you leave us

195
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:28,000
and Yanzhi Pavilion behind?

196
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,280
Go back first.

197
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,640
Where is Fang Zhuozhuo?

198
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,000
Lady Fang is not in the manor.

199
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,240
We've sent someone to look for her.

200
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:44,800
Not here?

201
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:50,360
We've been looking for Fang Qingcheng to no avail.

202
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:52,200
Now she suddenly appears.

203
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,340
It seems Fang Zhuozhuo

204
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,120
has seen through my plan.

205
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,440
If this is really Fang Qingcheng.

206
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,280
I'm afraid Xin'er

207
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,080
will never come back.

208
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,800
Young Master.

209
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,080
Our guess was right.

210
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,680
What should we do now?

211
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,300
Play out the whole act.

212
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,000
After all, Qingcheng

213
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,800
still needs to be alive to attend the Makeup Selection Ceremony.

